{
  "stem": "20616.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I understand that in one of those classes, the teacher did make remarks about Jews and some people became quite upset about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had to walk to school and it was quite a long walk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] well, to get into political-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, you-- I'll get into that a little later, I guess.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to the [GERMAN] Gymnasium, and that was on the Gutenbergplatz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Today that school is called the Gutenbergschule.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is not called the [GERMAN] Gymnasium anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Incidentally, that was the same school that my father attended, although the school at that time was at a different location.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, my father and I had the same teacher, my father when he was a rather young man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I had him in mathematics, he was ready for retirement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, he did retire after the first year or so that I had him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was extremely strict teacher and he also was a great protagonist of the cane, the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got to feel it very often.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He also gave us slaps on the face by holding us one ear and hitting us with the other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father remembered the same kind of punishment by the teacher.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But nothing was thought of it at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was considered part of the educational process.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first time I actually became aware of anti-Semitism was-- was in-- once while I was still in the elementary school, and that was the day of the boycott.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought it was the first boycott, but it happened in, I believe, August of 1933.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to school as usual.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did not know of any-- anything that was happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when we were dismissed, Herr [?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
